FBIS4-18693 "drweu068_p_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 GREECE Defense Minister Says EU Decision `Wrong Move' Defense Minister Says EU Decision `Wrong Move' NC0704190794 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1700 GMT 7 Apr 94 NC0704190794 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] Defense Minister Yerasimos Arsenis referred to the European Commission decision to refer Greece to the European Court over its measures against Skopje [The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia--FYROM] in the following way: [Begin Arsenis recording] This wrong move encourages destabilization in the region. It encourages the powers that be not to move toward settling the issue through dialogue and initiatives but to maintain their unreasonable positions. It is a move that ultimately praises the intransigent. [end recording]
